termAndEffectiveDates.name: Rate Stabilization per Service Component
termAndEffectiveDates.value: Rates as specified in this Pricing Schedule for each Host Service Component are stabilized until the end of its Minimum Payment Period (“MPP”).  The rates for the Virtual Network Functions Service Components are stabilized until the end of the MPP for the Host on which it resides.

termAndEffectiveDates.value: Non-stabilized prices as modified from time to time in applicable Service Publication or, if there is no such pricing, the pricing in this Pricing Schedule.
